{
  "stem": "9156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a film, much later, that I saw in the United States, and the man says, I'm a Jew by discrimination.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think that's a very good way of putting it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I will not go into all of the details.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a very important learning experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mona Specht, S-P-E-C-H-T, who later became very famous after the war working in the Republic, helping with the United Nations for children and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mina Specht said to me, you'd better go and study again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You are capable of doing this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is-- when somebody from the 'movement' said it, I listened a little more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I started at the University of Hamburg, studying psychology, history, philosophy, and especially education.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wanted to go into elementary school because that's where the poor children were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have to say that the most exciting thing at the University, for me, was, first, that it was clean.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I have-- and all my life, I say, rich people don't understand what it is to live in dirt all of the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this was really exciting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was clean, but it was also eating what you could get.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And studies at Hamburg were exciting, were superb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Psychology, especially because that was William Stern, who was known, also, in the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was-- by the way, William Stern certainly was also Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But he was one of the psychology professors who had such an enormously wide view of psychology.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He didn't have to say, Freud is wrong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to tell, certainly, that we all grew up with all of this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he also gave us pros and cons on several sides.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was especially interested in child psychology.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I learned a lot about how to observe children.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
